                        <div class="col-md-9" >

                    

                    
	

                    <!--Sharepoint's placeholder-->

                    
	
	
	
	
	
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ><div style="text-align&#58;right;">
   <a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-outline" href="/ohcs/es/disaster-recovery/reoregon/acerca-de-reoregon/Pages/adquisicion.aspx" title="Enlace para traducir este sitio web al Español">Español</a><br></div><p>Correctly and legally purchasing (or “procuring”) goods and services is a critical component of overall compliance with federal rules and regulations, per 2 CFR 200. OHCS and any subrecipient or contractor receiving funding under the ReOregon grant must follow the applicable federal procurement rules.<br></p><p>In order to assist contractors and subrecipients, and to maximize transparency,&#160;OHCS has a&#160;CDBG-DR <a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/procurement-policy-cdbg-dr.pdf">procurement policy</a>.&#160;<br></p><p>In addition, OHCS will report on this page active ReOregon procurements.</p><h2>General OHCS ReOregon Contracts</h2><p> 
   <a href="https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/bidDetail.sdo?docId=S-91400-00004536&amp;external=true&amp;parentUrl=close">Program Management Services RFP</a></p><p> 
   <a href="https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/bidDetail.sdo?docId=S-91400-00004571&amp;external=true&amp;parentUrl=close">Disaster Recovery System of Record RFP</a></p><p> 
   <a href="/ohcs/housing-assistance/disaster-recovery/Documents/OHCS-PRR-23-53-Record1-7322-CDBG-DR-SOR-Neighborly-Services-Agreement-REDACTED.pdf">Disaster Recovery System of Record Contract</a></p><p> 
   <a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/Documents/DRR%20Program%20Management%20Services%20No7470.pdf">Program Management Services Contract</a><br></p><h3 class="ms-rteElement-Heading3">Subrecipient Grant Agreements<br></h3><h4 class="ms-rteElement-Heading4">HARP Outreach and Intake<br></h4><ul><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/access-cdbg-dr-23-001-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">ACCESS Outreach Agreement</a><br></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/access-cdbg-dr-24-011-harp-intake-contract.pdf">ACCESS Intake Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/center-for-intercultural-organizing-cdbg-dr-23-007-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Center for Intercultural Organizing Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/csc_cdbg-dr-23-005-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Community Services Consortium Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/csc-cdbg-dr-24-014-harp-intake-contract.pdf">Community Services Consortium Intake Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/glide-revitalization-cdbg-dr-23-002-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Glide Revitalization Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/glide-revitalization-cdbg-dr-24-010-harp-intake-contract.pdf">Glide Revitalization Intake Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/jackson-county-community-ltrg-cdbg-dr-010-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Jackson County Community LTRG Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/lincoln-county-ltrg-cdbg-dr-23-008-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Lincoln County LTRG Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/mckenzie-valley-ltrg-cdgb-dr-23-009-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">McKenzie Valley LTRG Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/mckenzie-valley-ltrg-cdgb-dr-24-016-harp-intake-contract.pdf">McKenzie Valley LTRG Intake Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/nowia-cdbg-dr-023-003-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Natives&#160;of One Wind Indigenous Alliance Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/nowia-cdbg-dr-24-012-harp-intake-contract.pdf">Natives of One Wind Indigenous Alliance Intake Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/remake-talent-cdbg-dr-023-004-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Remake Talent Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/remake-talent-cdbg-dr-24-013-harp-intake-contract.pdf">Remake Talent Intake Agreement&#160;</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/santiam-hospital-cdbg-dr-023-006-harp-outreach-contract.pdf">Santiam Hospital and Clinics&#160;Foundation Outreach Agreement</a></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/santiam-hospital-cdbg-dr-24-015-harp-intake-contract.pdf">Santiam Hospital and Clinics Foundation Intake Agreement</a><br></li></ul><h4 class="ms-rteElement-Heading4">Intermediate Housing Assistance<br></h4><ul><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/access-iha-9023-cdbg-dr-agreement.pdf">ACCESS IHA Agreement</a><br></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/csc-iha-9024-cdbg-dr-agreement.pdf">Community Services Consortium IHA Agreement</a><br></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/lane-county-iha-9025-cdbg-dr-agreement.pdf">Lane County IHA Agreement</a><br></li><li><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/mwvcaa-iha-9026-cdbg-dr-agreement.pdf">Mid-Willamette Valley IHA Agreement</a><br></li></ul><h3 class="ms-rteElement-Heading3">Interagency Agreement<br></h3><p style="margin-bottom&#58;1.4rem;color&#58;#000000;"><a href="/ohcs/disaster-recovery/reoregon/about-reoregon/Documents/odhs-iaa-8010-disaster-case-mgmt.pdf">Oregon Department of Human Services Agreement</a>&#160;<br><br></p><h2>Open OHCS procurements</h2><p>None</p><h2>Resources</h2><p> 
   <a href="https&#58;//www.ecfr.gov/current/title-2/subtitle-A/chapter-II/part-200?toc=1">2 CFR 200</a><br></p><p>Single Audit&#58; A non-federal entity that expends $750,000 or more during the entity's fiscal year in federal awards must have a single audit conducted in accordance with 
   <a href="https&#58;//www.ecfr.gov/current/title-2/subtitle-A/chapter-II/part-200/subpart-F/subject-group-ECFRea73e47c9a286e6/section-200.514">CFR 200 Subpart F Audit requirements</a>.</p></div>
		</div>
